snippet: A man who confessed to the rape and murder of an 11-year-old girl was executed by lethal injection on Thursday, the Florida Department of Corrections said....

headline.print_headline: Florida Man Executed for 1994 Rape and Murder of Girl
headline.main: Florida Man Executed for 1994 Rape and Murder of Girl

lead_paragraph: A man who confessed to the rape and murder of an 11-year-old girl was executed by lethal injection on Thursday, the Florida Department of Corrections said.
